{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2b038ef311","title":"中共中央西南局规定干部在进行土地改革工作时的八项纪律","origin":" 中共中央西南局农村工作部编：《西南区土地改革运动资料汇编（下）》，重庆， 1954年。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c6819fee45","index":0,"year":1950,"month":9,"day":27,"articleId":"2b038ef311"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3a2aa8e6e3","type":"title","text":"中共中央西南局规定干部在进行土地改革工作时的八项纪律","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2b038ef311"},{"id":"5779585a2d","type":"paragraph","text":"一切参加土地改革工作的干部与工作人员、人民解放军的指战员、人民政府的工作人员，在土地改革期间，必须严格遵守下列纪律，以保证土地改革政策的正确实施：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2b038ef311"},{"id":"02dcbe6432","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）严格执行人民政府的土地法令，不准违犯。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2b038ef311"},{"id":"f9e5069f89","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）坚决拥护土地改革，不准包庇地主。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2b038ef311"},{"id":"4347cadcd8","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）廉洁奉公，不准贪污浪费、私吞果实或接受贿赂。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2b038ef311"},{"id":"d4ac940d8a","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）尊重人民民主权利，倾听群众意见和批评，不准欺压人民。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2b038ef311"},{"id":"c6bb14f0ba","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）一切重要问题和大家商量决定，然后推行，不要个人决定，强迫推行。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2b038ef311"},{"id":"c8a95d4bc3","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）依法律手续办事，不准乱捕、乱罚、乱打、乱杀。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2b038ef311"},{"id":"9f5a58027d","type":"paragraph","text":"（七）坚决服从上级指示，不准阳奉阴违。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2b038ef311"},{"id":"6af3df5a1e","type":"paragraph","text":"（八）严格执行请示报告制度，不准虚报情况，各自为政。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2b038ef311"},{"id":"2160b4f29e","type":"paragraph","text":"对上述各项，执行有功者予以奖励表扬，违反者分别情节轻重，予以应得处分。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2b038ef311"}],"page":{"id":"cf1abf45cd","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2b038ef311","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}